Description :

Space Dwarfs equipped for work in extreme harsh environments. The arms may need to be sanded or drilled slightly to fit well on the pegs. I included a body that you can add a head to, and an arm that can have different mining equipment or weapons added. Mirror the empty right arm to get a left arm.

Note: the vents on the back of the exo-armor do not print very well. I think I joined the parts incorrectly, I will update these files when I have fixed the problem.
